description: Since time immemorial it has been believed that only the strongest are worthy of wearing the shield, receiving its maximum power.\nUnfortunately, due to its weight - fragile magical hands experience difficulties at the moment of magical reading, due to which your Casting Speed and Speed are reduced.

name: Fragile Hands
description: Since time immemorial it has been believed that only the strongest are worthy of wearing the shield, receiving its maximum power.\nUnfortunately, due to its weight - fragile magical hands experience difficulties at the moment of magical reading, due to which your Casting Speed and Speed are reduced. However, protection against Dager and Bow weapons has been increased.

name: Shattered Shield
description: The madness of your speed and agility have always been ahead of you and your enemy, but only the presence of a shield can help you lose these skills forever, it is worth equipping it even once - you will immediately lose Running speed and a lot of dodge.

name: Lighter than Air
description: The thorny path of a warrior is not easy, but it has allowed you to master many defensive items so well that you can ignore some of their shortcomings. When using a Shield, your evasion does not decrease.

name: This is the Way
description: You feel that you have reached the heights after a long and arduous journey and are ready for rest, however, this is only the beginning of your path. You still need to prove your strength before the son of the Goddess Shilien, who is doing everything he can to delay your meeting. Because of this, the amount of experience you gain from battling monsters is reduced.
